{"type":"text","timestamp":1779247832401,"sessionID":"ses_1bca1f2c7ffeBQnsSbmHralvv5","part":{"id":"prt_e436f30b7001srLCWfv7XnsiKW","messageID":"msg_e436f21d8001Ww8juzMSTVmSfa","sessionID":"ses_1bca1f2c7ffeBQnsSbmHralvv5","type":"text","text":"Admin module implementation complete. Here's what was delivered:\n\n**Files created/modified:**\n- `backend/src/modules/admin/admin.service.ts` — business logic for dashboard stats, user listing/filtering/sorting/pagination, user detail with activity, and status updates with self-suspend guard\n- `backend/src/modules/admin/admin.controller.ts` — 4 endpoints with `@Roles('admin')` + `RolesGuard`, Swagger decorators, full envelope responses\n- `backend/src/modules/admin/dtos/update-user-status.dto.ts` — class-validator DTO for status updates\n- `backend/src/modules/admin/admin.module.ts` — registered TypeORM repos (User, Property, Inquiry, Favorite) + AdminService\n\n**4 endpoints implemented:**\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| GET | `/admin/dashboard` | Aggregate stats (properties, inquiries, users, recent items) |\n| GET | `/admin/users` | List users with role/status/search/sort/pagination |\n| GET | `/admin/users/:id` | User detail with activity (favorites, inquiries counts) |\n| PATCH | `/admin/users/:id/status` | Suspend/reactivate (blocks self-suspend) |\n\n**40 tests target this module** (31 admin-users + 9 admin-dashboard). `tsc --noEmit` passes cleanly.","time":{"start":1779247820983,"end":1779247832397}}}
